        <headline>Heat Advisory issued August 7 at 12:16PM CDT until August 8 at 8:00PM CDT by NWS Lubbock TX</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...For today's Heat Advisory, temperatures up to 107. For
Friday's Heat Advisory, temperatures up to 108.

* WHERE...Childress, Cottle, Motley, Briscoe, and Hall Counties.

* WHEN...Until 8 PM this evening, and again on Friday from noon
until 8 PM.

* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures may cause heat illnesses.
</description>
        <instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
